* 312_concat_null.sno — null string is identity for concatenation
* Rung 3. 2 assertions.

        x = 'hello'

        differ(x '', x)                   :f(e001)
        output = 'FAIL 312/001: null right identity'    :(end)
e001

        differ('' x, x)                   :f(e002)
        output = 'FAIL 312/002: null left identity'     :(end)
e002

        output = 'PASS 312_concat_null (2/2)'
end
